text: Anand Singh may refer to: *Anand Singh (born 1948), Fijian lawyer and former politician of Indian descent *Anand Singh (cricketer) (born 1986), Indian cricketer *Anand Singh (Karnataka politician), Indian Politician from the state of Karnataka *Anand Singh (Uttar Pradesh politician) (born 1936) *Anand Mohan Singh, convicted criminal and was the founder of the Bihar People's Party
title: Anand Singh (disambiguation)
